status/state of wifi connection			

#state : connected /disconnected
#status : show complete info of the network interfaces,
#device = network interface
#connection-name: refers to the connnection name i.e., vijay-punia	#check via >> nmcli device status  

nmcli
nmcli c
nmcli device show 		# show status of network interfaces
nmcli device show wlp3s0	# show status of the give interface
nmcli device status		# show state only
nmcli connection show		# shows the all network connections 
_________________________________________________________________________________________________
nmcli connection modify "netmax public" ipv6.addresses <ipv6-address> ipv6.method manual #changes the ip address
nmcli connection up "netmax public"	# apply the changed ip address

